26:36.228 --> 26:40.229
Toothbrush, toothpaste. An afro pick?

26:41.868 --> 26:45.468
Underwear?
Skittles, Daddy!

26:45.548 --> 26:48.429
Ha-ha!
You figured I forgot, huh?

26:50.429 --> 26:53.468
- You went shopping?
- Yeah, a little bit. Who this, baby?

26:53.549 --> 26:56.589
That's Lala.
Lala Bonilla, Jesus's lady.

26:56.669 --> 26:58.389
Lala Bonilla.

26:58.469 --> 27:02.670
Daddy, how'd you get out? I thought you
were gonna be away a long, long time.

27:02.751 --> 27:04.909
Can Daddy's little Boo Boo
keep a secret?

27:04.990 --> 27:06.949
Yeah.

27:07.030 --> 27:11.830
I'm out on a-- what you call like a...
work release program, baby,

27:11.910 --> 27:13.870
where's if l--

27:13.949 --> 27:16.989
- Well, I got a week to do a job.
- Meaning?

27:17.069 --> 27:20.310
