for the both of you.

31:50.160 --> 31:52.640
You hear me, Jesus?

31:52.720 --> 31:56.240
Like I said, son, you need to talk
to your daddy, see what he has to say.

31:56.321 --> 31:58.800
I told him I'd be here
at the Garden.

31:58.840 --> 32:03.080
Before you go now, I want you to use
