32:03.119 --> 32:05.762
This is what my daddy brought
up here from Mississippi.

32:05.841 --> 32:09.640
Now, you rub some of this here between
your wrist and your elbow, see,

32:09.721 --> 32:11.600
just like this here.

32:11.641 --> 32:14.481
